uctiť bohov.

383
00:24:55,060 --> 00:24:57,670
Tvoja rodina nepríde?

384
00:24:57,670 --> 00:24:59,340
Neviem.
Nezaujíma ma to.

385
00:24:59,340 --> 00:25:00,260
Urobme si to po svojom.

386
00:25:00,260 --> 00:25:02,020
Poďme dnu.

387
00:25:02,910 --> 00:25:04,690
Nie, tadiaľto.

388
00:25:04,690 --> 00:25:06,160
Ešte trochu.
Poď.

389
00:25:06,160 --> 00:25:07,560
Ešte kúsok.

390
00:25:08,890 --> 00:25:11,330
Mami, ste chorá?

391
00:25:12,130 --> 00:25:14,720
Snažila som sa ju dobre vychovať...

392
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:16,970
A ona si otvorí obchod a
utečie z domu.

393
00:25:16,970 --> 00:25:18,310
Som rozrušená.

394
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:24,290
Eun Chul, aj ty si tu.
Ako si sa mal?

395
00:25:25,030 --> 00:25:26,200
Kto si?

396
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,510
No tak, Oppa...

397
00:25:27,510 --> 00:25:30,100
Som Bomina priateľka,
Young Mi.

398
00:25:30,100 --> 00:25:31,200
Bae Young Mi.

399
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:33,100
Často som chodila k vám domov.

400
00:25:33,100 --> 00:25:33,690
Och...

401
00:25:33,690 --> 00:25:35,170
Tá úžerníčka?

402
00:25:35,900 --> 00:25:39,490
