prácu nehanbíš.

405
00:25:48,370 --> 00:25:50,480
Akk si chorá, mala si zostať doma.

406
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,570
Prečo si prišla?

407
00:25:51,570 --> 00:25:53,180
Nie je to tak, že by si bola cudzia.

408
00:25:53,180 --> 00:25:55,950
