427
00:26:44,870 --> 00:26:46,020
Čo je to?

428
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:49,440
Zoznam mojich zákazníkov.

429
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:51,300
Musíš mať nejaký marketing.

430
00:26:51,300 --> 00:26:55,080
