440
00:27:43,580 --> 00:27:45,670
Preferujem...

441
00:27:45,670 --> 00:27:47,200
Moje zlatíčko, Bin...

442
00:27:47,870 --> 00:27:51,050
Nie, hanbím sa...
Ešte nie som pripravená.

443
00:27:51,770 --> 00:27:53,310
Vitajte.

444
00:27:53,310 --> 00:27:54,990
Toto nie je kaviareň?

445
00:27:55,700 --> 00:27:57,060
Je to práčovňa.

446
00:27:57,060 --> 00:27:58,090
Prepáčte.

